These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, adventure
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, fonseca
House: victorian, wooden
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy
2 different games are played: poker, go
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
5. the person playing go is the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the wooden house is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Transport      | tram        | jet-ski |
| Movie-Genre          | adventure  | sports     |
| Cigar         | fonseca    | havana         |
| House           | victorian    | wooden |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | rock     |
| Flower           | poppy      | begonia    |
| Game         | go | poker          |

