2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, vegafina
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, cherry
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, august
House: gothic-revival, palace
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| City         | boston      | edinburgh       |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | vegafina |
| Food   | cherry      | blueberry        |
| Beverage   | milk         | hot-chocolate        |
| Flower   | dahlia    | amaryllis       |
| Birthday           | august        | november          |
| House     | palace          | gothic-revival    |

