.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, drama
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, pop
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, prince
2 different games are played: domino, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
2. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Pet      | cat | goldfish  |
| Movie-Genre          | drama   | disaster   |
| Music-Genre         | pop | house   |
| Flower           | daffodil        | begonia   |
| Color   | aquamarine      | blue |
| Cigar         | prince    | cain  |
| Game     | domino       | poker      |

